fields.subject: Ciparette Paper Clarification
fields.content:
Dear Mr Egressy,
Please clarfy the relationship; if any, between the following:
Olsenske Designation
Hungary Doslonation Garman Designation
Cigarette paper Pandema 18
Grade A
H25/0.5OPISTPTCF?
Cigarette paper Pandema 25
Grade B
H25/00SOPISTPCIF?
Plugwrap Rz7
PW 27 or PWNPi27mm
PWNP/28
We think that some of these may ba the same, but the infomatlon that wes sent t0 US from your factory Is not always consistent as far as nomenclature or supplier name (for example, Olpa vs Olsanske):
Please supply & supplier reference number for the Tann tipping used on Kossuth Filter;
The size Is not enough information:
We also still need a sample of the trlacetin that you use from Akzo Chemical:
